---
# Enaga project clang-format configuration.
# Style: Google C++ Style Guide targeting C++26.
# https://google.github.io/styleguide/cppguide.html
#
# Standard: Latest — tells clang-format to parse using the newest C++ syntax
# it supports, which aligns with the project's C++26 compiler standard.

Language:     Cpp
Standard:     Latest

BasedOnStyle: Google
